  Config: Interface & privacy
  Composer, transcript, privacy, and TUI behavior.

  Search Interface & privacy settings
› [*] Paste burst detection      Detect fast pasted input before inserting it into the
                                 composer.
  [ ] Hide reasoning summaries   Hide agent reasoning events from the transcript.
  [ ] Show raw reasoning         Show raw reasoning content when the model emits it.
  [*] Animations                 Show spinners, shimmer, and other TUI motion.
  [*] Tooltips                   Show first-run tips and contextual TUI hints.
  [*] Analytics                  Allow analytics across product surfaces on this
                                 machine.
  [*] Feedback                   Allow feedback collection from the TUI.
  [*] Unstable feature warnings  Show warnings for enabled under-development features.

  Right or Enter opens; Space toggles; Left or Esc goes back
